udents of peace operations, conflict management, policing, security studies and IR in general"--cProvided by publisher.  a16 4320aUnited NationsxPeacekeeping forces. 0aInternational police. 0aPeace-buildingxInternational cooperation. 0aConflict managementxInternational cooperation. 0aInternational relations. 0aSecurity, International. 0aRoutledge studies in peace and conflict resolution.  aJZ 4971 H86 2015c1hUAAU-Bi0162035180221  aJZ 4971 H86 2015wLCc1i0162035180221lON_SHELFmUAAUGp$150.00rYsYtBOOKu10/29/2014  aJZ 4971 H86 2015wLCc1i0162035195062d3/15/2017e2/27/2017lON_SHELFmUAHSSn3p$150.00rYsYtBOOKu11/26/201401ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n79021345